 />\nBtw唔太熟獸醫，都係問多啲人好啲"},{"pid":"a6fa785dc7036cf6cef98b0962cb2f13156ec3ef","tid":2327663,"uid":57439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4f1823e1c0fca9eeec605e84e6a5d9148c4f204","tid":2327663,"uid":244279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d31a62d4c81f22c5998c089f8daf1fb56d58c8f4","tid":2327663,"uid":57439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:42:10.000Z","msg":"去過北區, 朋友介紹, 跨區咁睇<br />\n覺得好好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T18:12:35.000Z","msg":"想問點樣好法？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:07:55.000Z","msg":"收費平, 隻貓要做手術<br />\n朋友果隻係荃灣享和做近兩萬, 北區收一萬內 (強調: 享和都係一間好好既獸醫)<br />\n<br />\n第一次見面, 除左手術細節仲問左d 行為問題<br />\n到做手術果次醫生會問返<br />\n<br />\n手術後, 醫院會打電話問返情況<br />\n<br />\n個人就好滿意"},{"pid":"c67c658310495d3f52d4ac5ec4222bb3b51675c9","tid":2327663,"uid":244279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7542f8ae2b7fe20146e5874fca30dec7853f73a4","tid":2327663,"uid":225696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T23:16:09.000Z","msg":"北區個陳齊禮醫生我睇過，幾好人，但好多人排<br />\n同埋食完藥有問題，啲護士都肯收影片幫你免費問其他醫生<br />\nBtw唔太熟獸醫，都係問多啲人好啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"所以上黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家都係做下基本檢查、打下針 試下好唔好先"},{"pid":"aaa0726a84d10955885e6095650fee7b7c044774","tid":2327663,"uid":244279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6fa785dc7036cf6cef98b0962cb2f13156ec3ef","tid":2327663,"uid":57439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4f1823e1c0fca9eeec605e84e6a5d9148c4f204","tid":2327663,"uid":244279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d31a62d4c81f22c5998c089f8daf1fb56d58c8f4","tid":2327663,"uid":57439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:42:10.000Z","msg":"去過北區, 朋友介紹, 跨區咁睇<br />\n覺得好好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T18:12:35.000Z","msg":"想問點樣好法？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:07:55.000Z","msg":"收費平, 隻貓要做手術<br />\n朋友果隻係荃灣享和做近兩萬, 北區收一萬內 (強調: 享和都係一間好好既獸醫)<br 